{"tid":736791,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(會live)德國五日團(2日係飛機度)","createTime":"2018-07-10T13:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T17:53:00.000Z","uid":189911,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2ea8c9ea5dafab16977b7d138ab12d4130ded341","tid":736791,"uid":189911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T13:18:46.000Z","msg":"跟學校去，唔好期待太多，盡量多圖。第一次出國，好緊張。BTW,12/7 23:20鐘機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72890a5af8a3146c10418b707c6b06ac070c19b3","tid":736791,"uid":189911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T13:20:43.000Z","msg":"打錯，無買卡，live唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，番到酒店即刻update<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b9b3e919f49bb26ca369cb89259c2ead63589d","tid":736791,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T13:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed39fba791c6cb38531cd8fa557b8ce180d1fc38","tid":736791,"uid":189911,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2b9b3e919f49bb26ca369cb89259c2ead63589d","tid":736791,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T13:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T13:23:44.000Z","msg":"係濛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6306ab9a6c7973f4433d4f924e6570e7287324","tid":736791,"uid":48762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:45:57.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"6775550e6c415fb6715d8b8b8494f5f9720b494b","tid":736791,"uid":189911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T09:52:20.000Z","msg":"依家出門口"},{"pid":"fc72a35e984d299a58cfaa1263235a4f4834f9cd","tid":736791,"uid":189911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T14:22:28.000Z","msg":"7：24到到飛機場，但係明明8：20先集合。同frd去到大家樂食咗個肉醬意，佢比咗杯红豆冰比我飲。<br />\n  食完之後，點名,check in。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/222150_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F222150_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=79e0ff27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後發生咗件媽呀好柒(想知再問)嘅事。11：05分嘅機，9：35開始鳩等<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/222223_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F222223_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=82d3c180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/222225_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F222225_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9f31a885&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e3256577a0825ca5546e082e08fad51f4e5c920","tid":736791,"uid":10793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T21:22:35.000Z","msg":"咩團有得去德國咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab286de2edf4a97c9bb3792d19b9ce8dc3a5423","tid":736791,"uid":189911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e3256577a0825ca5546e082e08fad51f4e5c920","tid":736791,"uid":10793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T21:22:35.000Z","msg":"咩團有得去德國咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T19:04:38.000Z","msg":"跟學校西史"},{"pid":"ab657d3b994682b57b60021743cbb1378efbff6c","tid":736791,"uid":189911,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T19:18:32.000Z","msg":"10:56分上咗機，一開頭有啲混亂。五至六分鐘後就settle down咗，其實我覺得上機前應該編好座位先囉......跟住，發覺無耳機，差啲嚇死。後尾先派番。。。<br />\n派飛機餐嘅時侯，我話要豬。味道中規中矩。第一次坐噉長時間嘅班，真係人都癲。最on9係飲咗2杯齊啡，想訓都訓唔到。。。<br />\n05：22到慕尼黑機場。。好累<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/030533_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F030533_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a81186a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/030538_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F030538_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6620ad06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/030542_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F030542_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=91488401&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n07:45準時上旅游巴，個位比較闊，架車比較寛躺。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/030949_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F030949_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=cd4bcf19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/030953_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F030953_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4a54f0f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 之後我哋到咗奧兹威爾集中營。由於個集中營主要係教育同講歷史背景嘅，加上個阿叔嘅濃厚德國口音嘅英文。所以悶到喊出嚟，但係其實個位置係幾有feel<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/031052_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F031052_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9a7413db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/031204_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F031204_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=41fd0abd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n午飯係西餐，three set <br />\n頭盤係湯，有蛋同埋啲香菜，少少辣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/031827_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F031827_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e09de26f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90a9dc34ad2cbbd90580efe77360fcace8fe1c22","tid":736791,"uid":103531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:51:47.000Z","msg":"依家d學校d團咁正既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c6b69ff2562cfbe5a28d24f35879b155b7a31b","tid":736791,"uid":189911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90a9dc34ad2cbbd90580efe77360fcace8fe1c22","tid":736791,"uid":103531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:51:47.000Z","msg":"依家d學校d團咁正既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:23:56.000Z","msg":"要交功課"},{"pid":"6d261e32406a82e340387e2d0969325f9791db1c","tid":736791,"uid":189911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:27:27.000Z","msg":"琴晚食中餐，無嘢好講<br />\nday 2<br />\n早餐食酒店自助餐，之後今日第一個行程就係去新天鵝堡，由於呢個地方嘅交通比較尷尬，附近沒有順便的景點，因此好少遊客會特意去，不過我呢個團有安排到<br />\n一落車，導遊去買飛，附近有一個湖，個景唔錯，我哋留係度打卡"},{"pid":"d31f7ceda6daa4dd07551098b0a37a5bf5988e6f","tid":736791,"uid":15251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2c6b69ff2562cfbe5a28d24f35879b155b7a31b","tid":736791,"uid":189911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90a9dc34ad2cbbd90580efe77360fcace8fe1c22","tid":736791,"uid":103531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:51:47.000Z","msg":"依家d學校d團咁正既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:23:56.000Z","msg":"要交功課"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T08:54:47.000Z","msg":"要交功課都抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71abe599998154849db7851880cbc1d716651cf","tid":736791,"uid":189911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d31f7ceda6daa4dd07551098b0a37a5bf5988e6f","tid":736791,"uid":15251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2c6b69ff2562cfbe5a28d24f35879b155b7a31b","tid":736791,"uid":189911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90a9dc34ad2cbbd90580efe77360fcace8fe1c22","tid":736791,"uid":103531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:51:47.000Z","msg":"依家d學校d團咁正既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:23:56.000Z","msg":"要交功課"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T08:54:47.000Z","msg":"要交功課都抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T19:15:23.000Z","msg":"$19xxx"},{"pid":"cd03c0f77d611e23c4ed23ccc366cf675b5ebaad","tid":736791,"uid":189911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T19:18:33.000Z","msg":"之後坐穿巴上山，首先係條橋影咗幾張，老實講，個位一般同埋好多人<br />\n之後去食飯，餐飯同琴晚差不多，仲難食啲。不過間餐廳出面賣雪糕就有驚喜，mověnpick一大球都係&euro;1.8。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/16/031642_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F031642_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=09377ed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/16/031650_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F031650_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a350dd3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後就入新天鵝堡内部參觀，為保護展品，堡內完全禁止拍照，所以無相睇。新天鵝堡係由一個巴洛伐克國王興建，内裏的佈置主要和宗教和英雄人物有關，例如天鵝騎士和法國國王聖徒路維等。"},{"pid":"2141bd2f911815c10b27be4bf43d1e71b30f9564","tid":736791,"uid":89036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T21:26:45.000Z","msg":"集中營得咁少野講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我第一次去Dachau睇到好撚sad<br />\n之前都讀過唔少德國日本既二戰仆街野 連睇isis都冇乜feel<br />\n但當你去到集中營諗到你企果塊地係死過幾十/百萬人仲要睇埋d 紀錄片d屍體係好似禽流感殺雞咁疊到幾堆咁<br />\n真係好難頂<br />\n最痛心既係諗番德國人咁坦白面對自己民族既歷史<br />\n但中共連64同文化大革命幾千萬人死左連提都唔提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1007fc422716dd4a6ffcfb0495e3d6cd72a4fbf","tid":736791,"uid":189911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2141bd2f911815c10b27be4bf43d1e71b30f9564","tid":736791,"uid":89036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T21:26:45.000Z","msg":"集中營得咁少野講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我第一次去Dachau睇到好撚sad<br />\n之前都讀過唔少德國日本既二戰仆街野 連睇isis都冇乜feel<br />\n但當你去到集中營諗到你企果塊地係死過幾十/百萬人仲要睇埋d 紀錄片d屍體係好似禽流感殺雞咁疊到幾堆咁<br />\n真係好難頂<br />\n最痛心既係諗番德國人咁坦白面對自己民族既歷史<br />\n但中共連64同文化大革命幾千萬人死左連提都唔提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T21:47:45.000Z","msg":"之後我哋到咗奧兹威爾集中營。由於個集中營主要係教育同講歷史背景嘅，加上個阿叔嘅濃厚德國口音嘅英文。所以悶到喊出嚟，但係其實個位置係幾有feel, sorry呀"},{"pid":"15cbab8f1cb5ec2f21bd1082ed949e56b799aed7","tid":736791,"uid":141782,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T21:50:13.000Z","msg":"仲以為你歐洲過去<br />\n香港過去睇得三日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘥心機捱眼訓咪呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1289e20b5e916f69cc8f3a0dd35721fc532c69e4","tid":736791,"uid":194991,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T21:54:24.000Z"